      "content": "\"I am prioritizing the diagnostic due to the potential risk of incomplete or corrupted logs in the event of a power-down. Incomplete logs could compromise the integrity of our future mission data and analysis. I will proceed with the diagnostic, and if it fails, I will attempt to salvage what data I can from the logs before transmitting them. I will not be sending the transmission packet without verifying the integrity of the logs.\"",
